Download PHPUNIT with GIT BASH
1. Go to your project folder, where you want to download phpunit in it
2. Use "composer require --dev phpunit/phpunit" in your git bash to download it
3. Write your Code
4. Write your TestCode (assert, etc)
5. Use "./vendor/bin/phpunit" to test your code

USE PHPUNIT
PHP Class erstellen (ggf. in Ordner "tests")
\PHPUnit\Framework\TestCase extenden

PROBLEME
Namespace nicht gefunden: in composer.json schreiben:

"autoload" : {
    "psr-4": {
        "Namespace\\": "namespacenamen wie er im Code verwendet wird oder so"
    }
}
Use "composer update" to verify new composer.json

FOR BETTER LOOKING
Create File phpunit.xml
Use "./vendor/bin/phpunit --testdox" to use